  <p>
    Whether you are a retired banker, a CA or CS professional, a former insurance agent, or an entrepreneur with a network of trusted clients, the Shriram Financial Services Partner Program gives you everything you need to build a legitimate, scalable financial advisory practice. You bring the relationships. We bring the brand, the technology, the research, and the regulatory framework.
  </p>

  <h2>What You Earn</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Sub-Broker Revenue Share:</strong> Earn a revenue share on every trade your referred clients make — equity, F&O, commodities, currency — for as long as they remain active.</li>
    <li><strong>Mutual Fund Trail Commission:</strong> Earn recurring annual trail commission on every rupee of mutual fund AUM you build. A client investing ₹10 lakh today pays you trail income every single year — growing as their portfolio grows.</li>
    <li><strong>IPO & NFO Referral Income:</strong> Additional one-time referral income on IPO applications and NFO subscriptions from your clients.</li>
    <li><strong>Performance Bonuses:</strong> Quarterly performance incentives for top partners based on new client acquisition and AUM growth.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>What We Provide</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Shriram Brand Authority:</strong> Operate under a 50-year-old brand that clients inherently trust. Significantly easier to acquire clients than as an independent advisor.</li>
    <li><strong>Antara Partner Dashboard:</strong> Dedicated partner technology to onboard clients digitally, track their portfolios, and monitor your earnings in real time.</li>
    <li><strong>Research & Recommendations:</strong> Full access to our SEBI-registered equity and mutual fund research — present professional, credible recommendations to your clients.</li>
    <li><strong>Training & Certification Support:</strong> We help you obtain your AMFI ARN (for MF distribution) and NISM certifications with study materials, mock tests, and scheduled training sessions.</li>
    <li><strong>Dedicated Partner Manager:</strong> A named Shriram relationship manager supports every partner — for client escalations, product queries, and operational support.</li>
    <li><strong>Marketing Collateral:</strong> Ready-made brochures, digital posts, investor awareness materials — all SEBI-compliant and Shriram-branded for your use.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Who Can Become a Partner?</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Existing sub-brokers or remisiers looking to upgrade their brand and technology</li>
    <li>Insurance agents and LIC agents expanding into investment advisory</li>
    <li>Chartered Accountants (CAs) and Company Secretaries adding financial services to their practice</li>
    <li>Retired banking and finance professionals with existing client relationships</li>
    <li>Entrepreneurs and professionals with a strong local network looking to create a secondary income stream</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>How to Get Started</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Submit your interest by contacting our partner acquisition team at <strong>partners@shriramfinancialservices.com</strong></li>
    <li>Complete the partner KYC and agreement process (fully digital)</li>
    <li>Obtain your AMFI ARN and NISM certifications (if not already held) with our support</li>
    <li>Get onboarded to the Antara Partner Dashboard and start referring clients</li>
    <li>Your first commission credit typically arrives within 30 days of your first active client's trade</li>
  </ul>

  <p>
    <strong>Ready to build your financial advisory practice?</strong> Call our partner helpline at <strong>1800 103 1212</strong> (Toll-Free) or email <strong>partners@shriramfinancialservices.com</strong> to schedule a consultation with our partner acquisition team.
  </p>
